snippet.title: Best VGM 882 - Baten Kaitos Origins - The Broken Manas and My One and Only
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 576 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cO1UTkT6lf8
Best VGM 2006 - https://youtu.be/69142JeBFXM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube
Baten Kaitos Origins (2006)
The Broken Manas and My One and Only
Motoi Sakuraba
